==Both Catalan and Spanish==
===Etymology===
Perhaps from [[fullare]], in Latin 'to speed up', according to the Institut d'Estudis Catalans; or from [[follis]], in Latin 'bellows', according to the Real Academia Española.

===Verb===
'''follar'''

# To [[fuck]]
